## COOLING FAN MOTOR INSPECTION  


1. Verify that the battery is fully charged. (Refer to 01-17 BATTERY INSPECTION.)  


2. Disconnect the cooling fan motor connector.  


3. Connect battery positive voltage and an ammeter  


to the cooling fan motor connector.  


4. Verify that the cooling fan motor operates smoothly at the standard current draw.  



